title: No, the Israeli Health Ministry Didn’t Say the Pfizer Vaccine ‘Killed 40 Times More Elderly’ Than COVID-19
subtitle: Israel has undertaken an aggressive push to get its population vaccinated against COVID-19.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: The Israeli Ministry of Health said that the COVID-19 vaccine developed by Pfizer has "killed 40 times more elderly" people than the virus itself.
